EditCloseTabComponent(String) - Constructor for class fs.gui.EditCloseTabComponent
Creates a standard tab component that contains a label bearing the specified title and an activated close button represented by an icon.
A component created by this constructor will by default NOT forward any mouse clicks to the main panel or to any JTabbedPane
All necessary graphical resources will be loaded from the default resource path.

extractGroup(String, String) - Static method in class fs.xml.PolyglotStringTable
Extracts a group name from groupID in the following way:
- If groupID == null, this returns null
- If prefix == null this returns the highest order group name in group ID
- If groupID doesn't start with prefix, this returns null
- If groupID.equals(prefix), this returns null
- Otherwise this returns prefix + "." + the highest order group name in group ID after prefix
